phrases: TS
Even if it is really an aftereffect of Nirvash's weapon,
it is weird that it is still there after a week.
Quartz Gun.
That is what we call it.
You heard the man.
But do not you think it is weird?
Since ancient times, this light has been sighted near the Norwegian Vester islands.
It is known as the North Pole Light.
Legends say that it was first seen in the age of the Vikings.
What is the problem then?
Do not you think it is conceivable that the Quartz Gun damaged not only the present, but the past as well?
What are you saying?
If the past was affected, we would have experienced changes too.
We might have experienced them already.
Then this world, inclusive of our memories, is a continuation of the changed past.
There is no way for us to confirm the changes, though.
Ao, what are you doing?
I was wondering, if what you just said
Children do not need to worry about it.
Ao, leave it to us.
The consequences were unexpected,
but you made the right choice when you decided to fire the weapon.
Weapon...
Also...
Have you gotten the list of staff who showed abnormalities in the health checkup yesterday?
According to Hannah Mama: despite the rise in white blood cell count,
their composition is different.
Also, by looking at the x-ray results,
you can see a material identical to that of the Scub Coral.
The allergic reaction to trapar is a condition that has been known for decades.
This is an entirely different matter.
Not to mention similar cases have been reported around the globe since yesterday's Secret emergence.
I get it.
I will ask the American government and the WHO for their opinions first.
Is that good enough for you?
I think the first case of this condition was diagnosed in a girl from Iwato island, Okinawa.
Her, huh?
The Scub Coral is the enemy of mankind and the Earth!
Trapar's harmful to our body and it will cause the downfall of mankind!
There is been a lot more of these protests lately.
They are not Okinawans.
Huh?
Are not they protesting for the control of the trapar?
They claim that the G-Monsters are Gods who will save the world.
And that the Scub Coral is the root of all evil.
G-Monsters as Gods?
Trapar and plant corals do not belong in this world!
Johansson said so as well!
Calm down!
It is just smoke!
They are just trying to scare us!
Those bastards!
They killed him!
Johansson my ass!
Find out where those environmentalists are from!
What the
You are...
He is alive!
We have met before...
You are Ao's girlfriend, right?
Where is the injured person?
Why is a child here?
She is that terrorist!
What?
Stop!
Step away.
It is dangerous.
Hey...
What are you doing?
Cannot you hear the Scub Coral's voice?
The trapar does not belong to anyone.
It is the Scub Coral's.
Look this way!
I am testing the camera!
Nice!
Fleur, smile!
You girls really are the best!
So cute!
You girls are clearly better than your anime counterparts!
Please stop!
Guys do not care about 3DPD like us.
They prefer what Kanzaki draws over us.
You two are special!
Yeah!
You are not merely models for PiedPi, you knocked it to the top of popularity charts!
You two are the real knockers!
Please stop with the boob jokes.
People say we might get cancelled, but until autumn we should work
Cancelled?
You mean our show is getting cut?
We are still getting the highest amount of downloads, though.
You check that stuff?!
It is just a rumor!
They say our sponsors are getting pressured...
Getting pressured?
You know, because GenBlu kept the Quartz a secret,
people are saying PiedPi is just propaganda for a terrorist organization.
So you think what the Secret said is right?
Look at yourself.
You seem down for someone who just saved the world, kiddo.
I am not a kid.
Oh yes you are.
No matter how many times you ask,
the only IFO teams are the Pied Piper and the Harlequin.
I have never heard about Goldi-whatever.
I erased them.
Huh?
That weapon erased the Coral in Norway as if it is never existed.
For the same reason, those girls have never been born...
Cut the crap out!
You have been weird lately!
That sounds like what this book says.
The one you got from Japan...
A world without Scub Coral and Secrets.
Our country believes that it might be more than just a dream.
Is not this Johansson dude some shady prophet?
He says that the Scub Coral and the Secrets are twisting our world...
or I should say, our history.
The conspiracy theory is that governments know about it too.
He is been talking about another world for years.
And then ten years ago in Okinawa...
Okinawa?
He met a young boy near the Scub Coral after it had calmed down.
That young boy knew of another history as well.
Johansson adopted him and wrote down his story.
I hope you are not going to tell me that Germany and Japan won WWII!
It is not that drastic.
But without Scub Bursts, the world would be a more peaceful and flourishing place.
For example, in the history he saw, the Earth's population is over 7 billion.
What is the population now?
A bit over 3.5 billion.
The continuous Scub Bursts inside and outside of Siberia in 1908 dealt a huge blow to the Soviet Union and China.
Japan's reconstruction after the war was slowed by a Scub Burst in the capital.
These events never happened in his version of history.
How convenient.
Religion's different too...
Oh, and of course, trapar does not exist.
But they are using energy from nuclear fission instead.
Nuclear fission?
A Scub Burst near a nuclear reactor would cause unbelievable amounts of damage,
so nuclear energy development was cut off.
He is delusional.
Johansson claims that is the correct reality.
So does that Japanese official named Nakamura.
Then the third team that Ao's talking about is also from that world?
Georg, could you look something up for me?
Look for Chloe McCaffrey and Maeve McCaffrey in Ireland!
Can we do the three-man shot next?
Ao?
He became a fictional character, too?
Of.
Course.
The new male pilot stirs everything up as you try to control your shaking hearts!
Our hearts are not shaking.
But Ao has a childhood friend who became the enemy pilot!
How is that in the story too?
I oversee the script.
You do that too?!
So, where is Ao?
Say, Elena, you and Ao have been...
Yeah!
Chloe said that they moved there to work at the plant!
Chloe?
The sisters exist in Irish census records.
Girls with the name of Maggie Kwan have been found in Hong Kong and Singapore...
Nirvash changed history in the sense that...
they never became IFO pilots in the first place!
That is Johansson's theory of another version of history, correct?
Interesting.
Georg, did you just switch personalities?
Another history?
A choice of worlds?
Why did you want to take a day off so suddenly?
Just half a day will do!
Please!
Then we will tag along as bodyguards.
Hurray, vacation.
Hang on a second.
I did not know Ao had a penpal in Ireland.
Arrived at destination.
The McCaffrey bakery.
If Chloe and Maeve chose a life where they do not pilot IFOs,
they would be living happily without knowing about me...
That is an irrational conclusion.
You cannot be certain that they are living happily because they are not piloting IFOs.
Girls, if you are done with your homework, then help me out.
Come here!
Yes!
Ao, what is wrong?
Did not you want to find out the consequences of your actions?
Whether or not you have brought fortune upon them?
Ao.
I am the only one who understands you.
Our country has not requested action from Generation Bleu.
We do not permit your presence on our waters.
This Scub Coral was on the seabed and no country claimed ownership of it!
Due to its reactivation, trapar extraction has become possible,
so we are claiming the ownership of it.
You would have to negotiate with your neighboring countries before you can say that.
Besides, we will not know when a burst will happen since it is reactivated.
Are you planning to take that Quartz material again?
Or should I say steal?
Generation Bleu has been misleading the world!
What are you going to do if a Secret appears?
There are scientists who claim that Secrets are gone for good.
Scientists, huh?
Whoa.
Withdraw for now.
The UN warned us about the Quartz.
Our courses of action are limited.
But reactivated Scub are all over the world!
Are we being attacked?!
The Quartz Gun has gone berserk.
What?!
If you do not release it, the ship's frame will not hold.
But why?
Now it looks like we are the bad guys!
Fleur!
Ao, use of the Quartz Gun is not permitted!
You saw it, did not you?!
It moved on its own!
What the hell's going on?!
Are you ignoring our warning?!
It swallowed the Quartz!
This is a clear act of provocation!
Stop freaking following me!
Ao!
What the hell is with this thing?
We are not supposed to be using this.
This is it!
I have been looking for this!
Truth, stop!
Give it back!
Did not you throw it away, Fukai Ao?
That thing's dangerous!
It is not just a weapon!
It can change the world!
That is what I want!
Damn...
Ao...
Mom?
We meet again.
You have grown so much!
You are really my mom, right...
Ao...
Do you understand now...
About what happened to me?
Ten years ago, you took a giant Quartz...
And I jumped to another time-plane with it.
Another time-plane?
For the Quartz, time and space are the same.
But I could not control it.
I got caught up in an unstable time-plane, and I could not arrive at the destination.
For me, only a few days have passed since I took the Quartz.
But the Quartz came back!
Then you could come with me and
I cannot.
I am just briefly overlapping with this time-plane.
No!
I do not want that!
I will bring you back!
I can go to where you are, using that gun, right?!
I do not know.
I think that is what Renton... what your dad has been looking for.
But it is imperfect.
I will give it a try.
I will perfect that gun...
Then I will come find you!
I will not let anyone take it!
Mom, tell me!
Where are you?!
You are going to shoot?
Perfect!
Shoot me!
Shoot me and change the world!
You are the child of the Scub Coral.
I am Johansson's son.
Therefore, we have no choice but to fight!
It is fate!
I do not care about fate.
That is not the reason why I fight!
The Allied Forces, huh?
I cannot press the trigger.
If I did, something would change again!
I do not want that!
I am Niki Tanaka of the Allied Forces base on Okinawa.
Fukai
Ao, we are to take you into protective custody.
Protective custody?
You are more than what Generation Bleu can handle.
Do not you agree?
Ao, get away!
We are shooting!
Stop!
Fleur, Elena!
Ao...
The Allied Forces... America fought on our side against the Secrets!
You cannot shoot them.
To be continued.
La Vie en Rose
